m:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Наши тени падают</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le nostre ombre cadono</span></p><p begin="6.390" end="9.380" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="6.390" end="6.730">Where</span> <span begin="6.730" end="6.870">tr</span><span begin="6.870" end="7.180">u</span><span begin="7.180" end="7.320">th</span> <span begin="7.320" end="7.640">wa</span><span begin="7.640" end="7.790">s</span> <span begin="7.790" end="8.110">on</span><span begin="8.110" end="8.250">ce</span> <span begin="8.250" end="9.350">earn</span><span begin="9.350" end="9.380">ed</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在这曾探寻到真理的地方</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在這曾探尋到真理的地方</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">かつて真実を掴み取った場所へ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">한때 진실을 쟁취했던 그곳에</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Là où la vérité fut jadis acquise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Donde una vez se ganó la verdad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wo einst die Wahrheit errungen wurde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Onde a verdade um dia foi conquistada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Там где когда-то была обретена истина</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dove un tempo la verità fu conquistata</span></p><p begin="10.560" end="12.890" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="10.560" end="11.000">We</span> <span begin="11.000" end="11.310">won&apos;t</span> <span begin="11.310" end="11.470">f</span><span begin="11.470" end="11.840">or</span><span begin="11.940" end="12.890">get</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我们未曾忘却</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我們未曾忘卻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">決して忘れない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리는 잊지 않을 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Nous n&apos;oublierons pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No olvidaremos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wir werden nicht vergessen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não esqueceremos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мы не забудем</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non dimenticheremo</span></p><p begin="13.760" end="16.420" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="13.760" end="14.250">The</span> <span begin="14.250" end="14.620">les</span><span begin="14.620" end="15.030">son</span><span begin="15.030" end="15.170">s</span> <span begin="15.170" end="15.470">we</span> <span begin="15.630" end="16.390">learn</span><span begin="16.390" end="16.420">ed</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那些铭刻于心的教诲</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那些銘刻於心的教誨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">私たちが学んだ教訓を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리가 깨달은 그 교훈들을</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les leçons que nous avons apprises</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las lecciones que aprendimos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Lehren die wir zogen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">As lições que aprendemos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Уроки которые мы усвоили</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le lezioni che abbiamo imparato</span></p><p begin="17.930" end="20.250" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="17.930" end="18.860">Pe</span><span begin="18.860" end="19.150">tal</span><span begin="19.150" end="19.310">s</span> <span begin="19.310" end="20.250">bloom</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">繁花纵然盛放</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">繁花縱然盛放</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">花びらは咲き誇る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">꽃잎은 피어나지만</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les pétales éclosent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Los pétalos florecen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Blüten erblühen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Pétalas desabrocham</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Лепестки распускаются</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">I petali sbocciano</span></p><p begin="21.160" end="23.910" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="21.160" end="21.510">But</span> <span begin="21.620" end="22.090">they</span> <span begin="22.090" end="22.570">won</span><span begin="22.570" end="22.630">&apos;t</span> <span begin="22.630" end="22.920">a</span><span begin="23.020" end="23.890">men</span><span begin="23.890" end="23.910">d</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">却无法修补残缺的过往</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">卻無法修補殘缺的過往</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">されど何も償えはしない</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아무것도 바로잡아 주진 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mais ils ne répareront rien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Pero no enmendarán</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Doch sie heilen nichts</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mas não vão remediar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Но они ничего не исправят</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ma non porranno rimedio</span></p><p begin="25.200" end="31.200" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="25.200" end="25.340">D</span><span begin="25.340" end="26.260">raw</span><span begin="26.260" end="26.300">n</span> <span begin="26.300" end="26.520">a</span><span begin="26.680" end="27.740">gain</span> <span begin="29.010" end="29.390">in</span><span begin="29.390" end="29.920">to</span> <span begin="29.920" end="30.280">your</span> <span begin="30.380" end="31.170">win</span><span begin="31.170" end="31.200">d</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">只能再次被卷入你的流风之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">只能再次被捲入你的流風之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">再びあなたの風に引き寄せられて</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">다시 너의 바람 속으로 이끌려가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Attirée à nouveau dans ton vent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Atraídas de nuevo hacia tu viento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wieder in deinen Wind gezogen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Atraídas novamente para o seu vento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Вновь влекомые твоим ветром</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Trascinati di nuovo nel tuo vento</span></p><p begin="1:02.260" end="1:04.570" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:02.260" end="1:02.560">Our</span> <span begin="1:02.560" end="1:02.710">sh</span><span begin="1:02.710" end="1:03.180">a</span><span begin="1:03.180" end="1:03.470">dow</span><span begin="1:03.470" end="1:03.640">s</span> <span begin="1:03.640" end="1:04.570">fall</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">阴影悄然笼罩</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">陰影悄然籠罩</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">影が落ちゆく</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리의 그림자가 드리워</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Nos ombres tombent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nuestras sombras caen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Unsere Schatten fallen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Nossas sombras caem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Наши тени падают</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le nostre ombre cadono</span></p><p begin="1:05.470" end="1:08.430" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:05.470" end="1:05.810">Where</span> <span begin="1:05.810" end="1:05.950">tr</span><span begin="1:05.950" end="1:06